tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE survey_metadata (
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_date DATE,
    respondent_id INT,
    completion_status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE SurveyResponses (
    survey_id INT,
    respondent_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    answer TEXT,
    PRIMARY KEY (survey_id, respondent_id, question_id)
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyMetadata (
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_date DATE,
    respondent_id INT,
    completion_status VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE QuestionMetadata (
    question_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    question_text TEXT,
    qcategory_id INT,
    qtype VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE RespondentDetails (
    respondent_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    respondent_name VARCHAR(50),
    respondent_email VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE SurveyResponses (
    survey_id INT,
    respondent_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    response_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE SurveyCategories (
    category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name VARCHAR(50)
)
